data.description: This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath has an office plus a gameroom that could be 4th bedroom! 3 car garage with safe room inside. Beautiful hand scraped hardwood floors throughout living spaces, office and master bedroom. Surround sound in living, master and master bath and back patio. Huge island with extra storage! Stainless appliances. Outdoor fireplace plus an outdoor grill. 30x40 shop with door run fenced in area.
